                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">Sir!</p>\n            <p>I have wrote to <persName>Dr Wise</persName> the same<lb/> but he did not answer me,\n                tis,<lb/> as I know, the has a little <sic>enamo,<lb/>sity</sic> against me, on\n                account of a<lb/>\n                <add>Hebrew</add> who he gave <add>Hebrew</add> and freedom<lb/> to perform the\n                service Duties appertain,<lb/>ning our Holy <hi rend=\"underline\">Religion</hi>. I\n                will not<lb/> detain you,k with much writing, as I<lb/> know, you can employ your\n                time<lb/> to other purposes, but I thought<lb/> you might show my letter to<lb/>\n                <persName>Dr <sic>Ellowy</sic></persName> and I hope that the<lb/> gentleman will be\n                satisfied</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Remain yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <add>?</add>\n            </p>\n            <p>P. S.</p>\n            <p>I must make you <sic>aquainted</sic> with<lb/> that, I don't perform no more<lb/>\n                <placeName>Italy</placeName><add>?</add> services in the Synagogue.<lb/> and this\n                quarrel is nothing to me.<lb/> but, for the sake of <add>Hebrew</add> between<lb/>\n                <sic>booth</sic> parties, I have mentioned to you<lb/> the writing of <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> and<lb/>\n                <placeName><hi rend=\"underline\">Amsterdam</hi></placeName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
